      <h3>About</h3>
      <p>Goalmine is a football prediction website. Each week, 12 matches are picked and you enter your predictions for these games. You gain points based on how close your prediction was to the result.</p>

      <p>One match is designated the game of the week, and you have a joker which you can play on any of the other 11 games, both of which double your score for that match.</p>

      <p>There is an entry fee of &pound;1 per week.  The player with the most points each week wins a cash prize which is a proportion of the week's entries. The remaining money is banked into a <a href="/money/0">prize pot</a> for the player with the highest score across the league.</p>

      <p>The league will begin in week 305 and run for to the end of the season. As some people will unavoidably miss weeks (or sometimes avoidably&hellip;) then the <strong>top 30 scores</strong> only will count towards the league.</p>
      
