      <h3>Rules</h3>
      <ol>
        <li>The entry fee is &pound;1 per week.</li>
        <li>There will be one main prize for the player with the highest score at the end of the week. the first prize will be 75% of the total entry fees. The remaining 25% will be added to the league pot.</li>
        <li>Players must create an account to take part. To create an account you must be invited by an existing member.</li>
        <li>One match each week will be chosen as the Game of the Week (GotW). This match will score <strong>double</strong> points.</li>
        <li>Each week, players must nominate one match in each group as their joker,which will also score <strong>double</strong> points for that match.</li>
        <li>Results of the matches will be updated on the site as soon as possible following the game.</li>
        <li>Once a match has taken place,any prediction for that match cannot be changed, even if the site has not yet been updated with the final score.</li>
        <li>Match predictions can be made or amended any time up until the deadline</li>
        <li>Your joker match can be changed as many times as you wish up to the day the match takes place. Following that, the joker cannot be moved to another match in the week, even though unplayed matches can still be edited.</li>
        <li>Points will be awarded for each prediction as follows:
          <ul>
            <li><strong>5 points</strong> - Predicting the correct match score (e.g. Score: 2-1, Prediction 2-1)</li>
            <li><strong>3 points</strong> - Predicting the correct winning margin (e.g. Score: 2-1, Prediction 1-0)</li>
            <li><strong>1 point</strong> - Predicting the correct winner (e.g. Score: 2-1, Prediction 3-0)</li> 
            <li><strong>0 points</strong> - Any other result / no prediction entered</li>
          </ul>
          GotW and Joker matches double the above scores
        </li>
        <li>The player (or players) whose total number of goals predicted is closest to the actual number of goals, will receive a bonus score of <strong>3</strong> points.</li>
        <li>Final scores will be those at full-time. If a match goes to extra-time, then the final score at the end of extra-time will be counted. Penalty shootouts will <strong>not</strong> count towards the result nor the number of goals scored</li>
        <li>In any event that a match is not completed during the week, that match is null and void and will score zero points.</li>
        <li>The winner of each week will be the person with the highest score, following the final match. If there is a tie at the end of the week then the money will be shared equally.</li>
      </ol>

